      "id": "PopularPost22291",
      "post_content": "@Schlappi: [Lore Broker](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lore Broker) & [Urza's Guilt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Urza's Guilt) don't work the same way that Bloodletter Quill, because with those cards you draw and discard at the same time (at the resolution of the spell/ability), instead with bloodletter you put the counter when you play the ability, then you lose life when the ability resolves.  \n  \nVery nice card. I used it in a deck with Power Conduit and [Chisei, Heart of Oceans](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chisei, Heart of Oceans), and worked very well!  \n4.5/5",
